Pioneer Corp. Africa to Take Control of Unifreight Zimbabwe

-- B y   G o d f r e y   M a r a w a n y i k a   a n d   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-07-14T11:54:52Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-14/pioneer-corp-africa-to-take-control-of-unifreight-zimbabwe-1-.html
Pioneer Corp. (6773)  Africa Ltd. plans to
take control of Unifreight Zimbabwe Ltd. in a transaction worth
about $7.2 million, Chief Executive Officer Albert Ushe said.  “We are still waiting for final approval from the
Competition Commission,” Ushe said in an interview at his office
today in Harare, Zimbabwe’s capital.  Pioneer owns transport businesses in Zimbabwe,  South
Africa , Botswana and Mozambique.  To contact the reporters on this story:
Godfrey Marawanyika in Harare at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net ;
Brian Latham in Johannesburg at 
 blatham@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 